      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Separate your <strong>duck leg[s]</strong> from the <strong>white fat</strong> and <strong>duck</strong> <strong>jelly </strong>(you'll use these in different parts of the recipe!)</p><p>Add the <strong>white duck fat</strong> to a baking tray (or two!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
